canna|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
canna: canna (A Japanese character set input system)
canna:
canna: Canna provides a user interface for inputting Japanese characters.
canna: Canna supports Nemacs (Mule), kinput2, and canuum. All of these tools
canna: can then use a single customization file, Romaji-to-Kana conversion
canna: rules and dictionaries, and input Japanese in the same way. Canna
canna: automatically supports Kana-to-Kanji conversions; the conversions are
canna: based on a client-server model.
canna:
canna: http://www.nec.co.jp/japanese/product/computer/soft/cann
